track_notes: Follow the line of the fence until you meet the shooting track at SD 5646 5883 and go straight across it. Continue for 2.5 Km to reach the first trig point and large boulders.

Total time (including ops): 2h 15m. Maximum difficulty: Swiss Alpine Club Grade T2. Uncurated GPX which may contain navigation errors, detours and hazards. Additional route information may be available at www.m1hax.uk. Track data by Richard M1HAX licensed under Creative Commons BY-NC-SA.
